Our Story我們的故事

About Cremona關於克雷莫納

Cremona Music of Strings is a dedicated music studio in the heart of Setia Alam, Selangor. Born from a deep passion for classical strings and piano education, we have built a warm, professional environment where students of all ages discover the joy of music.克雷莫納弦樂音樂位於雪蘭莪士地亞拉姆的中心。源於對古典弦樂和鋼琴教育的深厚熱情，我們建立了一個溫馨、專業的環境，讓各年齡的學生發現音樂的喜悅。

Our experienced teachers follow structured, internationally recognised curricula — preparing students not only to play beautifully, but to love music for a lifetime.我們經驗豐富的老師遵循有條理、國際認可的課程——不僅培養學生優美地演奏，更讓他們終身熱愛音樂。

What We Offer我們的課程

Music Lessons for Every Stage每個階段的音樂課程

Whether you are picking up a bow for the first time or preparing for a competition, our experienced teachers guide you with structured, personalised instruction.無論您是第一次拿起琴弓，還是準備參加比賽，我們經驗豐富的老師都會以有條理、個人化的方式指導您。

Cello大提琴

Deep, resonant and expressive — our cello programme nurtures tone, technique and musical sensitivity from the very first lesson.深沉、共鳴而富有表現力——我們的大提琴課程從第一堂課開始培養音色、技術和音樂敏感性。

Singing聲樂

Vocal training covering breath control, pitch, tone and performance. Suitable for all ages — from beginner to advanced singers preparing for exams or recitals.聲樂訓練涵蓋呼吸控制、音準、音色和表演。適合所有年齡——從初學者到準備考試或音樂會的進階歌手。

Percussion打擊樂

Develop rhythm, coordination and dynamic control through structured percussion lessons. Covers a broad range of percussion instruments for all levels.透過有條理的打擊樂課程培養節奏感、協調性和動態控制。涵蓋各種打擊樂器，適合所有程度。

Marimba馬林巴琴

Specialised marimba lessons focusing on mallet technique, musicality and repertoire — from classical to contemporary pieces.專業馬林巴琴課程，專注於槌法技術、音樂性和曲目——從古典到當代作品。

Music Theory樂理

Structured music theory classes covering notation, harmony, ear training and more — up to ABRSM Grade 8. Available as group or one-on-one sessions.有條理的樂理課程，涵蓋記譜法、和聲、聽音訓練等——至ABRSM八級。提供小組或一對一課程。

Performances & Events演出與活動

Our Recital Hall我們的演奏廳

A dedicated performance space where students, families and music lovers come together to celebrate musical achievement.一個專屬的演出空間，學生、家長和音樂愛好者在此共同慶祝音樂成就。

01

Student Recitals學生音樂會

Regular recitals prepare students for exams and competitions while welcoming family and friends as audience.定期音樂會幫助學生備考和參賽，同時歡迎家人和朋友觀賞。

02

Masterclasses大師班

Opportunities for piano and strings masterclasses with visiting guest artists and educators.鋼琴和弦樂大師班，邀請客座藝術家和教育家參與。

03

Special Events特別活動

A vibrant venue hosting many events throughout the year for our growing musical community.一個充滿活力的場地，全年舉辦許多活動，服務我們不斷成長的音樂社群。
